kanfei (0.1.0~beta4) unstable; urgency=low

  * SI unit storage: all sensor data now stored in SI (°C, hPa, m/s, mm).
    Includes DB migration script (tools/migrate_davis_to_si.py).
  * Multi-driver support: all 6 hardware drivers recovered, refactored
    for SI SensorSnapshot, and tested. Ecowitt, Tempest, Ambient Weather,
    Vantage Pro/Pro2/Vue, WeatherLink IP, WeatherLink Live.
  * Driver selection UI: Setup Wizard and Settings > Station tab now
    support all driver types with connection-specific config.
  * Driver test framework: parametrized JSON fixture tests for all drivers.
  * SI regression tests: 17 tests verifying identical API output.
  * Fix spray advisor reading SI values as Davis native.
  * Fix Vantage archive parser: convert to SI units.
  * CONTRIBUTING.md with AI-assisted contribution policy.
  * Issue templates, PR template, AGENTS.md for non-Claude AI tools.
  * Updated README with backup/restore, driver catalog.

