kanfei (0.1.0~beta1) unstable; urgency=low

  * First beta release under the Kanfei package name.
  * Package renamed from davis-wx to kanfei — see migration guide for
    users upgrading from alpha.
  * Spray advisor rule engine included as open-source (no longer requires
    external package for basic go/no-go evaluation).
  * AI nowcast available as optional add-on via kanfei-nowcast package.
  * NWS forecast and alert clients restored as built-in features.
  * Station status polling with exponential backoff for faster recovery
    when logger daemon starts after the web application.
  * Fix empty .env values crashing Pydantic settings parser.
  * Pluggable hardware drivers: Davis (serial, Vantage, WeatherLink IP,
    WeatherLink Live), Ecowitt/Fine Offset, Ambient Weather, WeatherFlow
    Tempest — all awaiting community hardware validation.

